@{
    Layout = null;
}
<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN" "http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd">
<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
<head>
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=gb2312" />
    <title>设计师-@{@WorkContext.ShopConfig.SiteTitle}</title>
    @Html.Raw(WorkContext.ShopConfig.SEOKeyword)
    @Html.Raw(WorkContext.ShopConfig.SEODescription)
    <link href="@{@WorkContext.CSSCDN}/themes/default/plugins/font-awesome/css/font-awesome.min.css" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" />
    <link href="@{@WorkContext.CSSCDN}/themes/default/css/base.css" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" />
    <link href="@{@WorkContext.CSSCDN}/themes/default/css/dr.css" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" />
    <link href="@{@WorkContext.CSSCDN}/themes/default/css/designer.css" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" />
    <script src="@{@WorkContext.ScriptCDN}/scripts/jquery.js" type="text/javascript"></script>
    <script src="@{@WorkContext.ScriptCDN}/scripts/common.js" type="text/javascript"></script>
    <link href="@{@WorkContext.CSSCDN}/components/jsmodern/jsmodern.min.css" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" />
    <script src="@{@WorkContext.ScriptCDN}/components/jsmodern/jsmodern.min.js" type="text/javascript"></script>
    <script type="text/javascript">
        $(function () {
            jsModern.video("#video");

        });
    </script>
</head>
<body>
    @Html.Partial("_header")
    <div class="container" style="width:1100px;margin-top: 50px;">
        <div style="height:640px;">
            <div style="float:left;width:50%;">
                <h1 class="title">设计师</h1>
                <h2 class="subtitle">Vedantti</h2>
                <p class="content" style="padding-right:20px;">VEDANTTI珠宝公司的设计师，她是一个充满活力的年轻女孩，爱笑并热情洋溢。她创作的初衷是为了女性的自信微笑而精心打造。她热爱大自然、设计珠宝和任何关于艺术的事物，她也因此从中获得灵感。VEDANTTI是一个极具天赋的设计师，她很努力，以确保设计不仅受到人们的喜爱，更能得到爱戴和珍视。设计珠宝的愿望扎根于血统，也因为她出生于珠宝世家。</p>
            </div>
            <div style="float:left;width:50%;text-align:right;">
                <img width="493" height="657" src="../../images/myvedantti1.jpg" sizes="(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px" />
            </div>
        </div>
        <br /><br />
        <div id="video" style="width:700px;height:396px;">
            <video src="@{@WorkContext.ImageCDN}/themes/default/video/designer.mp4"></video>
        </div>
        <br /><br />
        <div>
            <img width="1100" height="374" src="../../images/myvedantti2.jpg" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" />
            <h4 class="subtitle">父亲的足迹</h4>
            <p class="content">继她父亲之后，VEDANTTI也进入了珠宝的世界，然而，她却创造了一个全新和独特的天地。与钻石和珠宝的接近使她认识到，要创造出一件珠宝，需要付出极大的努力，才能让佩戴者充满喜悦和幸福的感觉。她内心的快乐和创造力总是由钻石和珠宝引起的。凭借在创造过程中所需的努力、关怀和付出的时间，她更坚定了要设计出让人幸福的珠宝的信念，而这些珠宝能够与我们内心最深处沟通。</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    @Html.Partial("_footer")
</body>
</html></script>